description: PREMIER EASTSIDE LOCATION OFFERS DISCERNING 2 BEDROOM 2 BATH WITH GARAGE PARKING! THIS IMPECCABLE “SMART” HOME OFFERS AN OPEN LIVING FLOORPLAN WITH CUSTOM ITALIAN (SCAVOLINI) CABINETRY, “SUBZERO” AND “WOLF” APPLIANCE KITCHEN AND MASSIVE FLOATING ISLAND. DESIGNATED DINING AND LIVING ROOM WITH OVERSIZED WINDOWS PROVIDING INCREDIBLE NATURAL LIGHT. KING SIZED EN-SUITE BEDROOM INCLUDES BESPOKE BATH WITH OVERSIZED GLASS SHOWER, AND CUSTOM CALIFORNIA WALK IN CLOSET. ADDITIONAL FEATURES INCLUDE KING SIZED GUEST BEDROOM, LARGE PLANK OAK HARDWOOD FLOORS THROUGHOUT, ELECTRO LUX IN-UNIT LAUNDRY, CENTRAL AIR, SURROUND SOUND AND SECLUDED PRIVATE DECK SURROUNDED BY LUSH GREENERY. EXCLUSIVE PET FRIENDLY ASSOCIATION WITH 100% OWNER OCCUPANCY, LOW CONDO FEE, AND LEONARD PLACE BEING ONE OF SOUTHIE’S MOST COVETED HIDDEN GEMS, ADD TO THIS HOME’S APPEAL!
